PowerPlot - How to use
======================

PowerPlot is distributed as a static library. This version is the
GPLv3-version and is distributed as source code. For the commercial
version which does not force you to redistribute derivative works of
this library, please contact us directly by email.

In XCode, add the files from the 'lib' directory to your project. Then
include the main header file "PowerPlot.h" in all files that access
and use any component of PowerPlot.

For further documentation and support please visit the website
http://powerplot.nua-schroers.de


Written 2010-2012 by Dr. W. Schroers, NuAS http://nua-schroers.de
Published under the GPLv3, see file <gpl-3.0.txt>
